data.description: The large front porch will welcome you home each day.  Inside you will find an open floorplan, spacious rooms, extra-large "Sweet" kitchen and oh so much more.  What a great floorplan.  The abundant large windows fill the home with natural light offering the welcoming feeling of comfort.   Need a Man Cave or She Shed (or additional storage)?  There is a 13 x 16 shed with electricity and ac in the back. Location is convenient to Goodfellow Air Force Base and easy access to schools, ASU, downtown, shopping and medical.
